<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>dāng dì xiōng ruǎn ruò de shí hòu 迦南683</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 dāng dì xiōng ruǎn ruò de shí hòu, gōu xīn dòu jiǎo de shí hòu,
 wǒ zěn néng suí bō zhú liú, zěn néng suí bō zhú liú?
 měi tiān lái dào fù de miàn qián, hé fù qīn shuō xīn lǐ huà.
 fù a nǐ kàn jiào huì jīn rì de guāng jǐng, wǒ zhī dào nǐ xīn rú huǒ fén.
 wǒ xiāng xìn nǐ dīng hén de shuāng shǒu, huì yī gè yī gè de chān lā.
 wǒ xiāng xìn nǐ huì lián mǐn, shǔ yú nǐ de měi yī gè ér nǚ.
 wǒ xiāng xìn wǒ xiāng xìn nǐ huì tì wǒ men zhēng zhàn.
 wǒ xiāng xìn nǐ de cí ài, yǒng yuǎn bù huì jiǎn shǎo.</lyrics>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<hymn_number>683</hymn_number>
</song>